<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>英语学习系统部署方案</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 40px;
            color: #333;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #3498db;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
            padding-left: 10px;
        }
        h3 {
            color: #2980b9;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        code {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 2px 5px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-family: Consolas, monospace;
        }
        pre {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        table, th, td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        th, td {
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
        .note {
            background-color: #fff8dc;
            padding: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffeb3b;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .warning {
            background-color: #ffebee;
            padding: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid #f44336;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>英语学习系统部署方案</h1>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h2>1. 系统架构概述</h2>
        <p>英语学习系统采用前后端分离架构，主要包含以下组件：</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>前端</strong>：基于Vue.js的单页面应用（SPA）</li>
            <li><strong>后端</strong>：基于SpringBoot的RESTful API服务</li>
            <li><strong>数据库</strong>：关系型数据库（MySQL/PostgreSQL）</li>
            <li><strong>文件存储</strong>：用于存储视频、音频等学习资源</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>系统架构图</h3>
        <pre>
┌─────────────┐      ┌─────────────┐      ┌─────────────┐
│             │      │             │      │             │
│  用户浏览器  │ ──→ │  Nginx服务器 │ ──→ │  Vue前端应用 │
│             │ ←── │  (静态资源)  │ ←── │             │
└─────────────┘      └─────────────┘      └─────────────┘
                                                │
                                                ↓
┌─────────────┐      ┌─────────────┐      ┌─────────────┐
│             │      │             │      │             │
│   数据库    │ ←── │ SpringBoot  │ ←── │   API网关    │
│  (MySQL)    │ ──→ │   后端服务   │ ──→ │             │
└─────────────┘      └─────────────┘      └─────────────┘
                            │
                            ↓
                     ┌─────────────┐
                     │             │
                     │  文件存储   │
                     │  服务/CDN   │
                     │             │
                     └─────────────┘
        </pre>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h2>2. 环境要求</h2>
        
        <h3>2.1 硬件要求</h3>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>服务器类型</th>
                <th>CPU</th>
                <th>内存</th>
                <th>存储</th>
                <th>网络</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>前端服务器</td>
                <td>2核+</td>
                <td>2GB+</td>
                <td>20GB+</td>
                <td>带宽10Mbps+</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>后端服务器</td>
                <td>4核+</td>
                <td>8GB+</td>
                <td>50GB+</td>
                <td>带宽20Mbps+</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>数据库服务器</td>
                <td>4核+</td>
                <td>8GB+</td>
                <td>100GB+</td>
                <td>带宽10Mbps+</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        
        <h3>2.2 软件要求</h3>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>组件</th>
                <th>版本要求</th>
                <th>说明</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>操作系统</td>
                <td>CentOS 7+/Ubuntu 18.04+</td>
                <td>推荐使用Linux系统</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Node.js</td>
                <td>14.x+</td>
                <td>前端构建环境</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Nginx</td>
                <td>1.18+</td>
                <td>Web服务器和反向代理</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>JDK</td>
                <td>11+</td>
                <td>Java运行环境</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>MySQL/PostgreSQL</td>
                <td>MySQL 8.0+/PostgreSQL 12+</td>
                <td>数据库服务</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Docker</td>
                <td>20.10+</td>
                <td>容器化部署（可选）</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h2>3. 前端部署方案</h2>
        
        <h3>3.1 构建Vue应用</h3>
        <p>前端应用需要先进行构建，生成静态资源文件：</p>
        <pre>
# 安装依赖
npm install

# 构建生产环境版本
npm run build
        </pre>
        <p>构建完成后，将在<code>dist</code>目录生成静态资源文件。</p>
        
        <h3>3.2 Nginx配置</h3>
        <p>使用Nginx作为Web服务器部署前端应用：</p>
        <pre>
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name your-domain.com;
    
    # 前端静态资源目录
    root /path/to/your/dist;
    index index.html;
    
    # 处理单页应用路由
    location / {
        try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;
    }
    
    # API请求代理到后端服务
    location /api/ {
        proxy_pass http://backend-server:8080/api/;
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;
    }
    
    # 静态资源缓存设置
    location ~* \.(js|css|png|jpg|jpeg|gif|ico|svg)$ {
        expires 30d;
        add_header Cache-Control "public, no-transform";
    }
}
        </pre>
        
        <h3>3.3 HTTPS配置（推荐）</h3>
        <p>为保证系统安全，建议配置HTTPS：</p>
        <pre>
server {
    listen 443 ssl http2;
    server_name your-domain.com;
    
    ssl_certificate /path/to/cert.pem;
    ssl_certificate_key /path/to/key.pem;
    ssl_protocols TLSv1.2 TLSv1.3;
    ssl_ciphers HIGH:!aNULL:!MD5;
    
    # 其他配置同上...
}

# HTTP重定向到HTTPS
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name your-domain.com;
    return 301 https://$host$request_uri;
}
        </pre>
        
        <div class="note">
            <p><strong>注意</strong>：可以使用Let's Encrypt等服务获取免费SSL证书。</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h2>4. 后端部署方案</h2>
        
        <h3>4.1 SpringBoot应用打包</h3>
        <p>使用Maven或Gradle打包SpringBoot应用：</p>
        <pre>
# 使用Maven打包
mvn clean package -DskipTests

# 或使用Gradle打包
./gradlew build -x test
        </pre>
        <p>打包完成后，将在<code>target</code>或<code>build/libs</code>目录生成JAR文件。</p>
        
        <h3>4.2 应用配置</h3>
        <p>创建生产环境配置文件<code>application-prod.yml</code>：</p>
        <pre>
spring:
  datasource:
    url: jdbc:mysql://db-server:3306/e_learning?useSSL=false&serverTimezone=UTC
    username: db_user
    password: db_password
    driver-class-name: com.mysql.cj.jdbc.Driver
  jpa:
    hibernate:
      ddl-auto: none
    show-sql: false
    
server:
  port: 8080
  servlet:
    context-path: /api
    
# 文件上传配置
file:
  upload-dir: /path/to/uploaded/files
  
# 日志配置
logging:
  level:
    root: WARN
    com.yourcompany.elearning: INFO
  file:
    name: /var/log/e-learning/application.log
        </pre>
        
        <h3>4.3 部署方式</h3>
        
        <h4>4.3.1 直接运行JAR文件</h4>
        <pre>
java -jar -Dspring.profiles.active=prod e-learning-backend.jar
        </pre>
        
        <h4>4.3.2 使用Systemd服务（推荐）</h4>
        <p>创建系统服务文件<code>/etc/systemd/system/e-learning.service</code>：</p>
        <pre>
[Unit]
Description=E-Learning Backend Service
After=network.target

[Service]
User=appuser
WorkingDirectory=/opt/e-learning
ExecStart=/usr/bin/java -jar -Dspring.profiles.active=prod e-learning-backend.jar
SuccessExitStatus=143
TimeoutStopSec=10
Restart=on-failure
RestartSec=5

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
        </pre>
        
        <p>启动服务：</p>
        <pre>
sudo systemctl enable e-learning
sudo systemctl start e-learning
        </pre>
        
        <h4>4.3.3 Docker容器化部署</h4>
        <p>创建Dockerfile：</p>
        <pre>
FROM openjdk:11-jre-slim

WORKDIR /app

COPY target/e-learning-backend.jar app.jar
COPY src/main/resources/application-prod.yml /app/config/

EXPOSE 8080

ENTRYPOINT ["java", "-jar", "-Dspring.profiles.active=prod", "-Dspring.config.location=file:/app/config/", "app.jar"]
        </pre>
        
        <p>构建和运行Docker容器：</p>
        <pre>
docker build -t e-learning-backend .
docker run -d -p 8080:8080 --name e-learning-backend e-learning-backend
        </pre>
        
        <h3>4.4 多实例部署与负载均衡</h3>
        <p>对于高并发场景，可以部署多个后端实例，并使用Nginx进行负载均衡：</p>
        <pre>
upstream backend {
    server backend1:8080;
    server backend2:8080;
    server backend3:8080;
}

server {
    listen 80;
    server_name api.your-domain.com;
    
    location / {
        proxy_pass http://backend;
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
    }
}
        </pre>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h2>5. 数据库部署方案</h2>
        
        <h3>5.1 MySQL/PostgreSQL安装</h3>
        <p>安装数据库服务器：</p>
        <pre>
# MySQL安装（CentOS）
sudo yum install mysql-server
sudo systemctl enable mysqld
sudo systemctl start mysqld

# PostgreSQL安装（Ubuntu）
sudo apt update
sudo apt install postgresql postgresql-contrib
sudo systemctl enable postgresql
sudo systemctl start postgresql
        </pre>
        
        <h3>5.2 数据库配置</h3>
        <p>创建数据库和用户：</p>
        <pre>
# MySQL
CREATE DATABASE e_learning CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci;
CREATE USER 'e_learning_user'@'%' IDENTIFIED BY 'secure_password';
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON e_learning.* TO 'e_learning_user'@'%';
FLUSH PRIVILEGES;

# PostgreSQL
CREATE DATABASE e_learning;
CREATE USER e_learning_user WITH ENCRYPTED PASSWORD 'secure_password';
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON DATABASE e_learning TO e_learning_user;
        </pre>
        
        <h3>5.3 数据库优化</h3>
        <p>MySQL配置优化（<code>/etc/my.cnf</code>）：</p>
        <pre>
[mysqld]
# 内存设置
innodb_buffer_pool_size = 4G
innodb_log_file_size = 512M

# 连接设置
max_connections = 500
thread_cache_size = 128

# 性能优化
innodb_flush_log_at_trx_commit = 2
innodb_flush_method = O_DIRECT
innodb_file_per_table = 1

# 字符集
character-set-server = utf8mb4
collation-server = utf8mb4_unicode_ci
        </pre>
        
        <h3>5.4 数据库备份策略</h3>
        <p>设置定时备份任务：</p>
        <pre>
# 创建备份脚本 /opt/scripts/backup_db.sh
#!/bin/bash
TIMESTAMP=$(date +"%Y%m%d_%H%M%S")
BACKUP_DIR="/backup/mysql"
mkdir -p $BACKUP_DIR

# MySQL备份
mysqldump -u root -p'password' --single-transaction --routines --triggers e_learning > $BACKUP_DIR/e_learning_$TIMESTAMP.sql
gzip $BACKUP_DIR/e_learning_$TIMESTAMP.sql

# 保留最近30天的备份
find $BACKUP_DIR -name "e_learning_*.sql.gz" -type f -mtime +30 -delete
        </pre>
        
        <p>添加到crontab：</p>
        <pre>
# 每天凌晨2点执行备份
0 2 * * * /opt/scripts/backup_db.sh >> /var/log/db_backup.log 2>&1
        </pre>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h2>6. 部署流程</h2>
        
        <h3>6.1 部署准备</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>准备服务器环境，安装必要软件</li>
            <li>配置防火墙，开放必要端口（80, 443, 8080等）</li>
            <li>配置域名解析（前端和API可使用不同子域名）</li>
            <li>准备SSL证书（如需HTTPS）</li>
        </ol>
        
        <h3>6.2 部署步骤</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>部署数据库服务器
                <ul>
                    <li>安装数据库软件</li>
                    <li>创建数据库和用户</li>
                    <li>导入初始数据（如有）</li>
                    <li>配置数据库优化参数</li>
                    <li>设置备份策略</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>部署后端服务
                <ul>
                    <li>构建SpringBoot应用</li>
                    <li>配置生产环境参数</li>
                    <li>部署JAR文件或Docker容器</li>
                    <li>配置系统服务自启动</li>
                    <li>验证API服务可访问</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>部署前端应用
                <ul>
                    <li>构建Vue应用</li>
                    <li>配置Nginx服务器</li>
                    <li>部署静态资源文件</li>
                    <li>配置HTTPS（推荐）</li>
                    <li>验证前端可正常访问</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ol>
        
        <h3>6.3 自动化部署（CI/CD）</h3>
        <p>使用GitHub Actions或Jenkins实现自动化部署：</p>
        <pre>
# GitHub Actions工作流示例 (.github/workflows/deploy.yml)
name: Deploy

on:
  push:
    branches: [ main ]

jobs:
  build-and-deploy:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    
    steps:
    - uses: actions/checkout@v2
    
    # 构建前端
    - name: Setup Node.js
      uses: actions/setup-node@v2
      with:
        node-version: '14'
    
    - name: Build Frontend
      run: |
        npm install
        npm run build
    
    # 构建后端
    - name: Setup Java
      uses: actions/setup-java@v2
      with:
        java-version: '11'
        distribution: 'adopt'
    
    - name: Build Backend
      run: mvn clean package -DskipTests
    
    # 部署到服务器
    - name: Deploy to Server
      uses: appleboy/scp-action@master
      with:
        host: ${{ secrets.HOST }}
        username: ${{ secrets.USERNAME }}
        key: ${{ secrets.SSH_KEY }}
        source: "dist/,target/*.jar"
        target: "/tmp/deploy"
    
    - name: Execute Deployment Script
      uses: appleboy/ssh-action@master
      with:
        host: ${{ secrets.HOST }}
        username: ${{ secrets.USERNAME }}
        key: ${{ secrets.SSH_KEY }}
        script: |
          cp -r /tmp/deploy/dist/* /var/www/html/
          cp /tmp/deploy/target/*.jar /opt/e-learning/
          sudo systemctl restart e-learning
          sudo systemctl restart nginx
        </pre>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h2>7. 监控与维护</h2>
        
        <h3>7.1 日志管理</h3>
        <p>使用ELK Stack（Elasticsearch, Logstash, Kibana）或Graylog集中管理日志：</p>
        <pre>
# Filebeat配置示例 (filebeat.yml)
filebeat.inputs:
- type: log
  enabled: true
  paths:
    - /var/log/e-learning/*.log
    - /var/log/nginx/*.log

output.elasticsearch:
  hosts: ["elasticsearch:9200"]
        </pre>
        
        <h3>7.2 系统监控</h3>
        <p>使用Prometheus + Grafana监控系统状态：</p>
        <pre>
# Prometheus配置 (prometheus.yml)
scrape_configs:
  - job_name: 'spring_boot'
    metrics_path: '/actuator/prometheus'
    static_configs:
      - targets: ['backend:8080']
  
  - job_name: 'node_exporter'
    static_configs:
      - targets: ['node-exporter:9100']
        </pre>
        
        <h3>7.3 性能优化</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>前端资源CDN加速</li>
            <li>图片和视频资源使用对象存储服务</li>
            <li>数据库查询优化和索引设计</li>
            <li>应用缓存（Redis）减轻数据库压力</li>
            <li>定期清理临时文件和日志</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h2>8. 安全措施</h2>
        
        <h3>8.1 网络安全</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>配置防火墙，只开放必要端口</li>
            <li>使用HTTPS加密传输</li>
            <li>配置Web应用防火墙（WAF）</li>
            <li>定期更新系统和软件包</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>8.2 应用安全</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>实现JWT或OAuth2认证</li>
            <li>防止SQL注入和XSS攻击</li>
            <li>实现请求频率限制</li>
            <li>敏感数据加密存储</li>
            <li>定期安全审计</li>
        </ul>
        
        <div class="warning">
            <p><strong>警告</strong>：生产环境中不要使用默认密码，所有密码和密钥应妥善保管，不要硬编码在配置文件中。</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h2>9. 灾备与恢复</h2>
        
        <h3>9.1 数据备份</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>数据库定时备份（每日全量+增量）</li>
            <li>文件存储定期备份</li>
            <li>备份文件异地存储</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>9.2 恢复流程</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>准备恢复环境</li>
            <li>恢复最近的数据库备份</li>
            <li>恢复文件存储数据</li>
            <li>验证系统功能</li>
            <li>切换流量到恢复环境</li>
        </ol>
        
        <h3>9.3 高可用方案</h3>
        <p>对于需要高可用的生产环境，可以考虑：</p>
        <ul>
            <li>多实例部署 + 负载均衡</li>
            <li>数据库主从复制或集群</li>
            <li>跨区域部署</li>
            <li>自动故障转移</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h2>10. 部署检查清单</h2>
        
        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>检查项</th>
                <th>状态</th>
                <th>备注</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>服务器环境准备</td>
                <td>□</td>
                <td>操作系统、软件安装、防火墙配置</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>数据库部署</td>
                <td>□</td>
                <td>安装、配置、初始化数据</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>后端服务部署</td>
                <td>□</td>
                <td>构建、配置、启动服务</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>前端应用部署</td>
                <td>□</td>
                <td>构建、Nginx配置、静态资源部署</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>HTTPS配置</td>
                <td>□</td>
                <td>SSL证书安装、配置</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>监控系统部署</td>
                <td>□</td>
                <td>日志、性能监控</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>备份策略实施</td>
                <td>□</td>
                <td>数据库备份、文件备份</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>安全措施检查</td>
                <td>□</td>
                <td>防火墙、认证、加密</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>功能测试</td>
                <td>□</td>
                <td>登录、核心功能、API接口</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>性能测试</td>
                <td>□</td>
                <td>负载测试、并发测试</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
</body>
</html>